'''''Rookies: Rendezvous''''' is a daily [[Star Wars comic books|webstrip]] on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]], written and drawn by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]. The series began in February [[2006]], and the story is set in the [[0 BBY/Legends|same year]] as the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]].

